If you're getting memory errors, right click the Ultimate SD Upscale node > Convert Input to Widget > change both tile_width and tile_height to widget > set to a size that works for you (512,768,1024)
If you're using a NON union ControlNet, make sure the toggle below is DISABLED

I recommend downloading specific control nets rather than using the union one, this can be done via the model manager or from hugging face.

Pose - OpenPoseXL2.safetensors (Search in model manager)

Depth - control-lora-depth-rank256.safetensors (Search in model manager)

Lineart - mistoLine_fp16 (Download from HF)

https://huggingface.co/TheMistoAI/MistoLine/blob/main/mistoLine_fp16.safetensors
